+# Word Garden
+
+Word Garden is a friendly terminal word-guessing game. Guess the hidden word before the garden runs out of water. It is like Hangman, but with plants instead of gallows.
+
+## Overview
+
+Word Garden is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous "Hello World" project for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a friendly terminal interface.
+
+## How to Play
+
+You're tending a small word garden. Each correct letter guess helps the plant grow. Each incorrect guess costs one unit of water and allows weeds to appear. Reveal the entire word before the garden runs out of water to win!
+
+### Rules
+
+- The game selects a random secret word and hides it with blanks.
+- You guess one letter at a time.
+- **Correct guess**: The letter is revealed wherever it appears in the word. The garden grows. No water is lost.
+- **Incorrect guess**: The letter is recorded, water decreases by one, and a weed appears.
+- **Repeated guess**: No penalty, but you're reminded you've already guessed it.
+- **Win**: Reveal all letters in the word before water runs out.
+- **Lose**: The water runs out before you've guessed the complete word.
+
+## Running the Game
+
+### Basic Usage
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden
+```
+
+This starts a game at the default difficulty (Normal).
+
+### With Options
+
+```bash
+# Easy mode (8 water, words 4-6 letters)
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy
+
+# Hard mode (4 water, words 7+ letters)
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard
+
+# ASCII mode (no emoji, for terminals without emoji support)
+python3 -m word_garden --ascii
+
+# Combine options
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard --ascii
+```
+
+### Difficulty Levels
+
+| Difficulty | Water | Word Length |
+|---|---:|---:|
+| Easy | 8 | 4–6 letters |
+| Normal | 6 | 5–8 letters |
+| Hard | 4 | 7+ letters |
+
+## Example Game Session
+
+```text
+🌱 Word Garden
+
+Word:     _ _ _ _ _ _
+Guessed:
+Water:   6/6 💧💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:   0
+
+Guess a letter: a
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:     _ A _ _ _ _
+Guessed:  A
+Water:   6/6 💧💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:   0
+
+Guess a letter: z
+
+No match. A weed appears.
+
+Word:     _ A _ _ _ _
+Guessed:  A Z
+Water:   5/6 💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:   1 🌿
+
+Guess a letter: r
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:     _ A _ _ E _
+Guessed:  A R Z
+Water:   5/6 💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:   1 🌿
+
+(continue guessing...)
+
+🌻 Bloom!
+
+You guessed the word: GARDEN
+The garden is thriving.
+```
+
+## Features
+
+- **Friendly theme**: Plants and gardens instead of gallows.
+- **Difficulty levels**: Easy, Normal, and Hard with varying word lengths and water amounts.
+- **Accessibility**: Built-in ASCII mode for terminals without emoji support; text labels always accompany numeric counts.
+- **Input validation**: Catches empty input, multiple characters, non-alphabetic characters, and provides helpful error messages.
+- **Clean terminal UI**: Renders game state clearly each turn.
+- **Graceful exit**: Ctrl-D (EOF) and Ctrl-C (KeyboardInterrupt) handled cleanly.
+
+## Requirements
+
+- Python 3.11 or later
+- Standard library only (no external dependencies)
+
+## Testing
+
+Run the test suite from the repository root:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m unittest discover -s tests
+```
+
+## Project Structure
+
+```
+word_garden/
+  __init__.py       # Public API exports
+  __main__.py       # Entry point for python3 -m word_garden
+  main.py           # Game loop and I/O (only module that touches stdin/stdout)
+  ui.py             # Terminal rendering (pure rendering, no I/O)
+  game.py           # Core game state and rules (pure logic)
+  words.py          # Word list and difficulty-aware selection
+```
+
+## Word List
+
+The game includes a built-in word list of ten garden-themed words:
+
+GARDEN, FLOWER, PLANET, PYTHON, TERMINAL, MEADOW, ORCHARD, VINEYARD, SEEDLING, HARVEST
+
+## Growth Stages
+
+The plant emoji grows with your progress:
+
+- **🌱 Seedling**: Game just started (no letters guessed yet)
+- **🌿 Leaf**: Making progress (some letters guessed)
+- **🌷 Tulip**: Nearly there (one or fewer letters remaining)
+- **🌻 Bloom**: Victory! (entire word guessed)
+- **🥀 Wilted Flower**: Defeat (ran out of water)
+
+In ASCII mode, a simple `*` marks the plant at each stage.
+
+## Design Notes
+
+Word Garden demonstrates:
+
+- Modular design with clear separation of concerns (game logic, UI, I/O)
+- Testable code with dependency injection for I/O
+- Input validation and error handling
+- Simple state management
+- Random word selection with difficulty filtering
+- Terminal rendering with accessibility in mind
+
+## Future Extensions
+
+Possible enhancements (not in the current version):
+
+- Category-specific word lists (plants, programming, wine, etc.)
+- Hint system
+- Score and streak tracking
+- Daily word mode
+- Configurable word list files
+- Colour terminal output
+- Save and load functionality
+- Web version
+- Multiplayer support
+
+## License
+
+This is a demonstration project for AI-assisted software development testing.
+
+---
+
+**Enjoy growing your garden!** 🌻
